snippet.title: Free Heroes of Might and Magic II Resurrection (must have for all Heroes 2 fans!!!)
snippet.description: fheroes2 – free implementation of Heroes of the Might and Magic II game engine with a plenty of delightful changes! For quick testing, you can download the prepared package with Heroes 2 Demo (contains Broken Alliance map). Download: http://heroes3wog.net/fheroes2-v0-8-4-update-heroes-of-might-and-magic-2-hd-mod/
